  m_text: Perched atop a rugged hill, this camp is trying to find sounds among the
    static. They haven't sent a signal in years, but they listen carefully to the
    silence of the barren land. Now they are trying to change the city with the machines
    in their hands.
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 11ef17dbd564e804c81a4564baac7198, type: 2}
