      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Individuals who meet all of the following criteria may be APPROVED.\n\n\u2022No
    inconsistencies are found in the documents.\n\u2022No abnormal discoloration
    of the skin is observed.\n\u2022Body temperature is between 36.0\xB0C and 37.5\xB0C.\n\u2022Light
    produces a normal shadow.\n\u2022The image inside the capsule appears normal."
