  m_text: "Even one of the following signs indicates that the individual may be a
    \u201CSuret\u201D, and additional questioning is required before making a decision.\n\n\u2022Inconsistencies
    in the information provided during questioning.\n\u2022The individual claims
    to be injured, but their gait or posture contradicts this claim.\n\u2022Yellow
    discoloration of the skin."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
